
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Owner permissions

* Group permissions

* Other permissions

* + (adds permission to a file or dir)

* - (remove permission to a file or dir)

* d (dir)

* - (file)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

0 - No Permission
1 - Execute
2 - Write
3 - Execute + Write
4 - Read
5 - Read + Execute
6 - Read + Write
7 - All Permissions

* Format - rwx

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

* chmod 755 file

* chmod u-x file (remove execute for user)

* chown root file (change owner, now root is owner)

* chgrp group file (change group)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------